abi popular mobilisation pm rose defence baghdad south obama sleeping n't wake gates irbil gates baghdad nothing iran support would taken whole gulf iraq sunni heartlands anbar province west baghdad iraqi state forces struggling may 2015 militants captured provincial capital ramadi time spread grip syria taking iconic city palmyra tadmur desert east homs clear signal organisation may dealt setbacks still height powers capable exploiting weaknesses found americans quietly busy preparing real war poured billions rebuilding iraqi army 2003 see much go pieces pressure much wrong foundations putting several thousand advisers focused training equipping key iraqi special forces counter-terrorism service cts otherwise known golden division play crucial role spearheading drive militants systematic lashback began anbar province eventual recapture ramadi end 2015 early 2016 grinding costly operation close coalition air support huge destruction displacement city largely sunni population also tensions deployment iranian-backed mainly shia militias core sunni areas though largely kept city recapture ramadi tightened noose around even iconic centre sunni sentiment nearby falluja militants fought two major battles americans 2004. government pm forces began closing around city early 2016 soon taking ramadi lot testing assessing americans allies working closely local forces clearly embarked comprehensive strategy degrade ultimately destroy wherever could found broad lines spelled february 2016 lt gen sean mcfarland commanding general coalition combined joint task force operation inherent resolve campaign three objectives destroy isil parent tumour iraq syria collapsing power centres mosul raqqa two combat emerging metastases isil tumour worldwide three protect nations attack next step road mosul battle falluja joined late may 2016 took month assaults bombardments air strikes complete civilians paying heavy price fighters deployed full range battle tactics snipers booby-traps suicide 